cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.NI 

This paper deals with the detection of malware using machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of machine learning algorithms also suggests that it could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the effects of concept drift on the algorithms, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and network security (cs.NI).
